Get My Payment Procedures

1. Make IRS account
2. go here https://www.irs.gov/individuals/get-transcript
    1. Reason Adjusted Gross Income
    2. Customer File Number: blank
3. Click most recent account transcript
4. See what it has for your address (Mine is abbreviated 1431 1)
5. Enter your address here to get the official USPS spelling: https://tools.usps.com/zip-code-lookup.htm?byaddress
6. Go to get my payment and put hyphens in your SSN and use the exact address (capitalization too). Only do the 5 digit zipcode
7. if you get thru and it requires you to enter your adjust gross income and everything, go back to step 2 and download your most recent return transcript
8. control + F for adjusted gross income and for your owed/refunded amount
